description:
This was doctor Fauci not to long ago but now all of a sudden the mask protects you & we must all start wearing them?? Here is my opinion on what this all about; This is all about control from the beginning to test just how quickly people will fall into line & follow their arbitrary ever evolving “rules” that are not based in any science. It’s training you to obey orders that don’t make sense. 
Cuomo said 66% of those who died or were hospitalized were those in “quarantine” at home. 19% from nursing hind & prison. Since learning this, did he ease restrictions? No

States that are opening up like Florida & Georgia are seeing 15%+ drops in hospitalization & deaths. Does this information cause these people to reconsider these deadly lockdowns? No

This Virus is fizzling our faster than those who wanted to exploit it for political reasons had hoped. So it keep this pandemic & the fear around it alive, they want everyone wearing the masks so the imagery of death & disease stays in the minds of people. 
The last thing these people want is a return not normality. 
#masks #wearamask #covid_19 #stayathome #faucifraud #firefauci #fauci #nwo
